785
00:44:19,740 --> 00:44:20,660
Pergilah.

786
00:44:28,870 --> 00:44:30,030
Jangan tengok saya.

787
00:44:30,030 --> 00:44:31,030
Saya tak boleh buang air kalau awak berdiri di situ.

788
00:44:33,220 --> 00:44:33,700
Okey.

789
00:44:40,950 --> 00:44:42,660
Jangan usik saya!

790
00:44:55,820 --> 00:44:56,590
Sayang?

791
00:45:57,780 --> 00:45:58,870
Kamu sudah bangun.

