00:49:02,870 --> 00:49:04,550
ke bandar besar seorang diri.

832
00:49:04,550 --> 00:49:05,820
Ibu dan saya tak dapat membantu

833
00:49:06,340 --> 00:49:08,030
apa-apa pun.

834
00:49:08,030 --> 00:49:10,430
Kami sentiasa rasa bersalah tentang itu.

835
00:49:13,180 --> 00:49:14,740
Dan awak, awak ada perwatakan itu.

836
00:49:14,910 --> 00:49:16,510
Nampak bijak di luar,

837
00:49:17,550 --> 00:49:18,620
tapi lembut dan degil di dalam.

838
00:49:19,820 --> 00:49:21,870
Sama seperti saya.

839
00:49:22,220 --> 00:49:23,910
Awak dah lalui banyak cabaran.

840
00:49:24,390 --> 00:49:25,340
Saya cuma…

841
00:49:26,510 --> 00:49:27,740
Kalau-kalau…

842
00:49:29,340 --> 00:49:30,470
Dan saya betul-betul maksudkan kalau-kalau.

843
00:49:31,180 --> 00:49:32,590
Kalau apa-apa berlaku,

844
00:49:32,780 --> 00:49:33,950
saya takkan risau

845
00:49:34,140 --> 00:49:35,820
tentang ibu awak.

846
00:49:35,820 --> 00:49:37,550
Saya tahu awak akan jaga dia.

847
00:49:40,700 --> 00:49:41,740
Tapi

848
00:49:42,950 --> 00:49:43,950
